## Why This Is Asked
Assess ability to design isolation-first, compliant, scalable SaaS on GCP.

## Key Concepts
- Multi-Region Spanner per-tenant for isolation
- Pub/Sub + Dataflow routing
- Private access with VPC Service Controls + Private Service Connect
- Per-tenant analytics datasets, auditability, DR strategy

